### List
This control allows the user to pick a value from a list of options.

Example config:
```JSON
"list": {
	"value": "",
	"label": {
		"en-GB": "List example"
	},
	"control": "core/list",
	"options": [
		{
			"value": "One",
			"label": {
				"en-GB": "One",
                "fr-FR": "Un"
			}
		},
		{
			"value": "Two",
			"label": {
				"en-GB": "Two",
                "fr-FR": "Deux"
			}
		},
        {
			"value": "Three",
			"label": {
				"en-GB": "Three",
                "fr-FR": "Trois"
			}
		}
	]
}
```

